    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "System Timetable\nEffective July 1, 1983\n16251\nNEW JET SERVICE TO\nSANTA BARBARA\nREDDING\nKLAMATH FALLS\nREDMOND/BEND\nPlus new Fresno and Los Angeles\nto Reno service",
